qLeft.desc:
Position from the left.
Corresponds to the first column.

qTop.desc:
Position from the top.
Corresponds to the first row.

qWidth.desc: Number of columns in the page. The indexing of the columns may vary depending on whether the cells are expanded or not (parameter qAlwaysFullyExpanded in HyperCubeDef).

qHeight.desc: Number of rows or elements in the page. The indexing of the rows may vary depending on whether the cells are expanded or not (parameter qAlwaysFullyExpanded in HyperCubeDef).
